flowchart TD
    A[User navigates to /login]
    B[Login Page is rendered]
    C[User enters credentials:<br>Username/Email & Password]
    D[User clicks 'Login']
    E[Dispatch login action]
    F{Backend validates credentials?}
    G[Success: Backend returns user profile<br>and sets HTTP-only cookies]
    H[Failure: Backend returns error message]
    I[Update global state with user data]
    J["Navigate to protected area (/profile)"]
    K[Display error message on login page]

    A --> B
    B --> C
    C --> D
    D --> E
    E --> F
    F -- Yes --> G
    F -- No --> H
    G --> I
    I --> J
    H --> K
